WEBVTT FILE

1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,588
After I got divorced, I thought a lot about the woman who used to work for us.

2
00:00:04,588 --> 00:00:08,008
How important her presence was

3
00:00:08,008 --> 00:00:11,595
how she helped me avoid a breakdown during the divorce.

4
00:00:11,595 --> 00:00:12,929
If she hadn't been there

5
00:00:12,929 --> 00:00:14,808
I wouldn't have been able to work,

6
00:00:14,808 --> 00:00:16,835
produce, become independent

7
00:00:16,835 --> 00:00:19,227
and I would not be the woman I am today.